{"tid":2018212,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［行動/香港人齊心多一次咁多］527 全港18區見","createTime":"2020-05-15T13:09:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-18T01:34:21.000Z","uid":41005,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f4a8f081e9ef0f05f1b3d58f263bfbcf993c4881","tid":2018212,"uid":41005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T13:09:17.000Z","msg":"見住612手足要坐4年你地既感受係咩<br />\n<br />\n呢一年辛辛苦苦經歷過捱過，受盡警暴/黑社會/藍絲暴力對待，法治淪為人治<br />\n<br />\n呢廿年香港一步一步陷入衰退，法治、教育、自由各方面全面崩塌，無一幸免<br />\n<br />\n流過既血、汗、淚水，記憶都唔會隨時間抹得走<br />\n<br />\n不安、憤怒、傷心充斥咗香港人一年<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">人本著自私既心，革命無可能會成功<br />\n<br />\n唯有齊心盡地一鋪先可以有機會扭轉局勢 <br />\n<br />\n香港人再無退路</span></span> <br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"7a6d446232a67e55d7db9e7c29a83c42a261105d","tid":2018212,"uid":74214,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T13:12:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i50QrE2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi50QrE2.jpg&h=612be980&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6CRW6E2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6CRW6E2.jpg&h=b128aabc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nCaACMJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnCaACMJ.jpg&h=5483f38a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gvpqfyo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgvpqfyo.jpg&h=346b8d01&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MzFACMK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMzFACMK.jpg&h=c5697ba7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uWZtXMK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuWZtXMK.jpg&h=26d53792&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VQB4v6K.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVQB4v6K.jpg&h=c80b59ca&s